column3: Completed build up of NEW system sn 0032.  Tested all sensor inputs successfully.  RF modem tested okay.  Installed new Iridium SIM card. Successfully tested GPS and XMIT functions with roof-mounted antennas connected inside lab.
Ran Current drain test for 2 days, 14.65mA Average.  Dumped FLASH RAM data file, which looked okay.
Installed SS metal standoffs on bottom of circuit board stack.
Current drain test after deployment at 0-23W, PT008, ran for 5 days, 14.50mA.
Successfully tested GPS and Iridium XMIT outside
Installed NEW O-rings, face seal & jam seal.
